**Describe the bug**
from server trying to send message every 10s to client. But it's not sending there is some error in code.

you can see how exactly the code is written here https://stackoverflow.com/questions/74610861/socket-io-not-able-to-emit-to-all-the-connected-clients

**To Reproduce**

